---
import OleloPhrase from "./ui/OleloPhrase.astro";
---
<section class="section bg-paper">
  <div class="container-x grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
    <div class="md:col-span-3">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-lava">Mission</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-9">
      <p class="font-display text-display-md md:text-display-lg leading-[1.05] text-ink"
         style="text-wrap: balance; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96;">
        We exist to give the people who feed Hawai‘i
        <span class="italic text-ulu">a wider doorway</span> — to their customers,
        to the trade, and to whoever <em class="italic text-lava">happens</em>
        to be hungry that night.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-stone text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
        That looks like a long-form podcast you can sit with for ninety minutes. A
        marketing curriculum vendors can actually use. And the unglamorous,
        permit-fee, zoning-rule, county-meeting work that smooths the road for
        everyone trying to do this for a living.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-10">
        <OleloPhrase haw="E ʻai i ka mea i loaʻa" en="Eat what you have — be grateful for the food in front of you." />
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
